    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营属于你的足球场地设施</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修复球场，接待玩家，并通过新增场地扩展你的业务。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与朋友一起玩</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最多4位朋友进行多人游戏，共同发展你的事业。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/2c3cadfd6ac3a375b079b939266b358c.poster.avif?t=1771019395\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/2c3cadfd6ac3a375b079b939266b358c.webm?t=1771019395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/2c3cadfd6ac3a375b079b939266b358c.mp4?t=1771019395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动态足球场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修复磨损的球场，更新场地并进行清洁。让你的顾客满意，同时提升你的业务质量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/b23a38237e94e57eadce38fe8e3d8fb5.poster.avif?t=1771019395\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/b23a38237e94e57eadce38fe8e3d8fb5.webm?t=1771019395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/b23a38237e94e57eadce38fe8e3d8fb5.mp4?t=1771019395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>合作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与朋友分担任务，共同建立一个完美的企业。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/d4b6259dbcb756108f11a6a6544e8695.poster.avif?t=1771019395\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/d4b6259dbcb756108f11a6a6544e8695.webm?t=1771019395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/d4b6259dbcb756108f11a6a6544e8695.mp4?t=1771019395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营一家商店</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >补充货架，设定价格，并出租足球鞋。在你的运动设施中管理一家完美的商店。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/d8013a90fc3c019bc67a00d57c031b91.poster.avif?t=1771019395\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/d8013a90fc3c019bc67a00d57c031b91.webm?t=1771019395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/d8013a90fc3c019bc67a00d57c031b91.mp4?t=1771019395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>扩展您的业务</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩建您的足球场综合设施，通过开放新区域吸引更多客户。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/146de56e7a42b965434bd407b7bf50c8.poster.avif?t=1771019395\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154800/extras/146de56e7a42b965434bd407b7bf50c8.webm?t=1771019395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
